The following configuration successfully builds the package:

Compilers
    - tested on OpenSUSE 13.2:
        GCC 4.8.1
        Intel C++ Composer XE 15.0
        
    - tested on Windows 10 TP:
        MinGW-w64/GCC 4.9.2
    
Third-party libraries:
    GSL 1.16
    OpenBLAS 0.2.13
    SuiteSparse 4.4.3
    sqlitepp 0.2            (included in libs/, works e.g. with sqlite3 3.8.3)
    CLN 1.3.4
    FFTW 3.3.4
    GiNaC 1.6.2
    HDF5 1.8.14
    
Optional dependencies:
    png++ 0.2.5             (included in libs/, works e.g. with libpng 1.6.6)
    OpenMPI 1.7.2
    OpenCL 1.2
    
Code documentation generation:
    Doxygen 1.8.5
